div.p: This chart documents the progress made so far in the collections of plant samples for the DToL project, from the 25-Aug-2019 to 03-Dec-2020. Out of 2746 target species, 232 have been collected. In terms of plant families - out of 260, 118 have been collected. There have been 11 duplicate collections. Overall, 243 specimens have been collected. The bar chart below splits these totals by vascular and bryophyte collections.
